+//! WAL Safety Verification Tests (AGENTS.md RULE 2)
+//!
+//! These tests verify that BeadsClient respects SQLite WAL safety requirements.
+//! Data loss from improper WAL handling is CRITICAL to avoid.
+
+#![cfg(test)]
